unnormalised: Soglea vevsaay dhoniank ek punnyad: Tumchea PAN card (zoxem, ABCDE1234F) tumchea Aadhaar cardak (zoxem, 1234 5678 9012) aakhri tarikhe adim zodo korunk visrunk naka, dend bhogchea khatir. Toxench, tumchem GSTIN (zoxem, 07AAACC1234B1Z0) sogllea vevaharan khatir lagim dovortat. Tumchem TAN (zoxem, DELA12345A) sudharun dovortat tech porim. Companyank, CIN (zoxem, U12345MH2000PLC123456) MCA lagim sogllim patravalli korchea khatir khub mhotvachem.
normalised: sogllea veapari dhoniank ek sochnni! tumchea P-A-N cardak (zoxem, A-B-C-D-E ek don tin char F) tumchea Aadhaar cardak (zoxem, ek don tin char panch so sat atth nau shuna ek don) mech korunk visrunakat, dandd thambovnk nimanne tarikhe adim. toxench, tumchem G-S-T-I-N (zoxem, shuna sat A-A-A-C-C ek don tin char B ek Z shuna) sogllea vevharan khatir tayar dovrat. tumchem T-A-N (zoxem, D-E-L-A ek don tin char panch A) sudharit dovrat. companyankhatir, C-I-N (zoxem, U ek don tin char panch M-H don hazar P-L-C ek don tin char panch so) M-C-A kodden sogllea filean khatir chodd mhotvachem.
